---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Auto Configuration
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- @EnableEncryptableProperties - not needed when using jasypt-spring-boot-starter

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Set Master Password & algorithm
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- jasypt.encryptor.password (required)
- jasypt.encryptor.algorithm (default: TODO)

- more configs: https://github.com/ulisesbocchio/jasypt-spring-boot

